[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="LevelChunkDef" load_steps=8 format=3]

; Cinder Vaults — Pincer Reliquary.
; W3-T7 Stage 4 — S2 chunk authoring (ticket 86c9y7ygj).
;
; Role: high-pressure procedural-fill chunk. The S2 analog of s1_room07
; (Pincer Hall) — bruiser-dominant trial gauntlet. Two Bone-Catalysts apply
; melee pressure while a Sunken-Scholar holds rear position for ranged
; threat.
;
; Mob mix: 2 Bone-Catalyst (flanking pincer positions per the s1_room07
; multi-charger precedent) + 1 Sunken-Scholar (rear caster — the player
; must choose: rush the scholar through the pincer, or clear bruisers
; while eating ranged shots).
;
; Ports: WEST entry + EAST exit.

